something to eat.

67
00:03:55,974 --> 00:03:58,716
All right, now,
your dad's out of the room.

68
00:03:58,760 --> 00:04:00,414
You gonna tell me
what really happened?

69
00:04:04,331 --> 00:04:05,810
Those there
are puncture wounds.

70
00:04:05,854 --> 00:04:07,508
